[
  "The richest grocer in Spain, Juan Roig is president and majority owner of supermarket giant Mercadona.",
  "Roig, his brother Fernando and wife Hortensia Herrero, also billionaires, bought the chain in 1981 from the Roigs' father when it had just 8 stores.\r\n",
  "By 2006, Mercadona had opened its 1,000th store; it now has more than 1,600 locations, including 10 stores in Portugal. ",
  "Mercadona's 85,000 employees receive a 25% share of the company's pretax profits."
]